OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FIn May's local elections, Labour's
OL,7,Fimplied vote share was 24.3% and
OL,8,FReform's was more than 50%.
OL,10,FLast night Labour's Andy Burnham
OL,11,Freceived about 55% of the vote, a full
OL,12,F20 percentage points more than
OL,13,FReform's Robert Kenyon.
OL,15,FSo Burnham returned what looked like a
OL,16,Fsafe Reform seat back into a Labour
OL,17,Fseat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
