OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781873291
OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FPerhaps as significantly, he also
OL,7,Fincreased Labour's vote share by ten
OL,8,Fpercentage points vis a vis Reform
OL,9,Fcompared with the 2024 general
OL,10,Felection, which his predecessor Josh
OL,11,FSimons won.
OL,13,FIn other words, there is zero
OL,14,Fambiguity around last night's result.
OL,16,FThe so-called Burnham factor turned
OL,17,FLabour's humiliation in relation to
OL,18,FReform into Labour victory, at least
OL,19,Fin this north-western constituency.
OL,26,@pD@Wqp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
