OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FAnd Reform cannot blame Restore
OL,7,FBritain's Rebecca Shepherd to Kenyon's
OL,8,Fright for splitting the vote.
OL,10,FIn the end she received only around
OL,11,F7%, so her vote aggregated with
OL,12,FKenyon's was still well short of
OL,13,FBurnham's.
OL,15,FSo for Keir Starmer personally, this
OL,16,Fresult was about as bad as it could
OL,17,Fhave been - despite him saying this
OL,18,Fmorning that "voters chose Labour's
OL,19,Fcampaign of hope and optimism over
OL,20,Fdivision and hate".
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
