OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FEvery Makerfield voter knew that
OL,7,FBurnham's motive for running in their
OL,8,Fconstituency was to become an MP with
OL,9,Fthe purpose of launching a coup to
OL,10,Freplace Starmer as prime minister.
OL,12,FThat was the "change" he was promising
OL,13,Fthem. They overwhelmingly endorsed him
OL,14,Fand his ambition to seize the reins of
OL,15,Fpower.
OL,17,FObviously under our parliamentary
OL,18,Fsystem, 25,000 Burnham voters in Wigan
OL,19,Fhave no formal power to turf out
OL,20,FStarmer.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
