OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FBut they do have the power in
OL,7,Fpractice, because very large numbers
OL,8,Fof ministers and of Labour MPs think
OL,9,FStarmer's time is up, and Burnham is
OL,10,Fsignificantly more popular with Labour
OL,11,Fmembers than Starmer.
OL,13,FThere is almost no realistic scenario
OL,14,Fin which Burnham does not now become
OL,15,FBritain's next prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
