OL,3,CRobert Peston: Burnham almost has the
OL,4,Ckeys to Downing Street
OL,6,FThe question is precisely when, - and
OL,7,Fwhether there is an orderly consensual
OL,8,Fhandover from Starmer to him, or
OL,9,Fwhether Starmer is as good as his word
OL,10,Fand will insist on fighting Burnham,
OL,11,Fand probably Wes Streeting too, in a
OL,12,Fsix-week leadership contest.
OL,14,FBurnham will give Starmer the weekend
OL,15,Fat least to take stock, in the hope
OL,16,Fthat a chaotic and divisive contest
OL,17,Fcan be avoided.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
